 />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"佢發脾氣都好過完全冇反應，連發你脾氣，去傾既機會都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"首先多謝巴打<br />\n<br />\n我唔知佢嗰種好消極又悔氣嘅態度算唔算係脾氣<br />\n即係佢會話 算喇，我唔想傾，唔傾喇，唔好搞住我類似嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n所以我都唔敢去chur住佢話要傾，我只係想佢靜落嚟嗰陣先睇下仲有無彎轉<br />\n<br />\n我而家都唔知會唔會仲有機會，但係我唔想有遺憾"},{"pid":"141f89e68d03c1239e29e997e377fca26d42177b","tid":624841,"uid":46927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"即係咩事"},{"pid":"210d871bcb9cef78ba5e946ed223420dcc60759c","tid":624841,"uid":82064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"141f89e68d03c1239e29e997e377fca26d42177b","tid":624841,"uid":46927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"即係咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"巴打你好<br />\n<br />\n你嘅問題係咪話我同佢中間發生左咩事先會咁？"},{"pid":"8fd537ce167c8e91b00270ac619541608a1ef188","tid":624841,"uid":150894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:28:38.000Z","msg":"比完機會你之後咪又係耐左就唔記得當初既承諾"},{"pid":"0e0e61b27dd34fdf112d740f4a1b73b6c6de42a8","tid":624841,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"其實講咁多野都唔知你衰乜 點都好 <br />\n等佢冷靜完 搵返佢傾啦"},{"pid":"bb7b854930dd7ae3c281b2f922c145ef9de12b18","tid":624841,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210d871bcb9cef78ba5e946ed223420dcc60759c","tid":624841,"uid":82064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"141f89e68d03c1239e29e997e377fca26d42177b","tid":624841,"uid":46927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"即係咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"巴打你好<br />\n<br />\n你嘅問題係咪話我同佢中間發生左咩事先會咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:29:42.000Z","msg":"咩事做左導火線"},{"pid":"79e97fbdcc84806732fdc1c6e3d6f6a93a3c660d","tid":624841,"uid":82064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fd537ce167c8e91b00270ac619541608a1